{
  "texts": [
    "In relation to Chinese-language encyclopedia corpora, in addition to the Chinese version of Wikipedia, there is also the Baidu baike corpus 23.",
    "It covers almost all knowledge domains.",
    "TigerBot-wiki (Chen et al, 2023c) is filtered from the data of Baidu baike.",
    "Multi-category corpora contain two or more types of data, which is beneficial for enhancing the generalization capabilities of LLMs.",
    "During model pre-training, one can either choose existing open-source multi-category corpora directly for pre-training or select multiple single-category corpora for a certain proportion of mixing."
  ]
}